&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Business or other relevant fields is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1-2&amp;nbsp;years of business-to-business (B2B) sales&amp;nbsp;experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience selling software-as-a-service (SaaS) solutions -OR- selling product/services to enterprise healthcare companies is strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with prospecting, cold calling, customer outreach via phone and email, utilizing CRMs (preferably HubSpot), etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive spirit with a drive to succeed&amp;nbsp;in a quota/metric-driven sales environment&lt;/li&gt;
